<blockquote>Prevail Academy recently partnered with <a data-interception="off" href="https://www.gcfb.org/" target="_blank">Gleaners Community Food Bank</a> and <a data-interception="off" href="https://www.fox2detroit.com/" target="_blank">Fox 2 News</a> to host an annual Double Your Donation Day to help fight hunger in Metro Detroit this holiday season. Gleaners, headquartered in Detroit, aims to achieve a hunger-free community in southeast Michigan by providing access to nutritious food and related resources. </blockquote>
<a class="nha-btn nha-btn-primary" href="/schools/prevail-academy/en/Blog/Prevail-Academy-Partners-with-Gleaners-Food-Bank">Continue Reading</a>
